item.title: Available subscriptions
item.description: Available subscriptionsWhen provisioning services for an account, you need to include certain values with each API call to specify a particular service. The subscriptions available to you will vary depending on your current partner program ( Self-Service Partner Program External link icon Open external link or Enterprise Resellers and MSP Program External link icon Open external link ). The following values are samples and not exhaustive. For the complete list of subscription values available to you, make an API call to the zone subscriptions or account subscriptions endpoints.
